# Project Structure

The codebase is organized into the following key directories:

## Source Code Organization

- [src/](mdc:src/) - Main C++ implementation files
  - [src/com_hooks/](mdc:src/com_hooks/) - COM interface hooking implementation
  - [src/frame/](mdc:src/frame/) - DirectX frame extraction
  - [src/hooks/](mdc:src/hooks/) - Windows API and DirectX hooking
  - [src/memory/](mdc:src/memory/) - Memory scanning and pattern matching
  - [src/shared/](mdc:src/shared/) - Shared memory transport
  - [src/signatures/](mdc:src/signatures/) - DirectX function signatures
  - [src/tests/](mdc:src/tests/) - Internal unit tests
  - [src/virtual_camera/](mdc:src/virtual_camera/) - Virtual camera implementation

## Headers

- [include/](mdc:include/) - C++ header files
  - [include/com_hooks/](mdc:include/com_hooks/) - COM hooking declarations
  - [include/hooks/](mdc:include/hooks/) - API hooking declarations
  - [include/memory/](mdc:include/memory/) - Memory operations
  - [include/signatures/](mdc:include/signatures/) - Pattern definitions
  - [include/virtual_camera/](mdc:include/virtual_camera/) - Virtual camera interfaces

## Python Code

- [python/](mdc:python/) - Python utilities and tools
  - [python/capture/](mdc:python/capture/) - Screen capture utilities
  - [python/tools/](mdc:python/tools/) - Injection and utility scripts
  - [python/accessibility/](mdc:python/accessibility/) - Accessibility control modules
  - [python/tests/](mdc:python/tests/) - Python-based tests
  - [python/examples/](mdc:python/examples/) - Example usage scripts

## Documentation and Support Files

- [docs/](mdc:docs/) - Documentation
- [tests/](mdc:tests/) - C++ test code
- [scripts/](mdc:scripts/) - Batch files and automation scripts
- [DLLHooks/](mdc:DLLHooks/) - DLL project files for Visual Studio
